{"tid":2167672,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"痱滋警遇襲案 情報組警員被官指作供「即興咁講」","createTime":"2020-08-21T09:02:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-21T09:12:51.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f49133b9953714f7fc758d668d55c39eb423ad3a","tid":2167672,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T09:02:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200821/6RX7Y4DUTNBBNHEU3MOY3CJBKE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200821%2F6RX7Y4DUTNBBNHEU3MOY3CJBKE%2F&d=fUB9jTkReJc3fMEQQRliu02FGjryiJR74P7%2B0uEOyUg%3D&h=e22c9a4a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200821%2F6RX7Y4DUTNBBNHEU3MOY3CJBKE%2F&h=5b2765cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200821/6RX7Y4DUTNBBNHEU3MOY3CJBKE/</a><br />\n<br />\n去年6月26日大批反送中示威者包圍警察總部。當日有便衣警員聲稱欲往警總上班時，遭多名示威者追打。一名地盤工人事後被控襲擊傷人及暴動罪，案件今在區域法院續審。負責分析錄像的警員今出庭作供，仔細分析新聞片段中各人的行為，惟遭辯方質疑庭上證供並無寫進書面供詞；法官郭啟安亦同意辯方說法，指警員口供寫得不詳盡，並且「即興咁講」。<br />\n<br />\n法官郭啟安同意辯方說法，指警員口供寫得不詳盡，使辯方今日才首次聽到證人的意見，「連第一證人（張金福）自己都冇講過打多咗一拳」，並指證人「即興慶咁講」，的確令辯方措手不及。<br />\n<br />\n郭官向主控稱「想佢講，就申請押後做多份口供」，並指「你作為主控，你都見到口供唔詳細，就應該指引OC（案件主管）寫返長佢，咁樣好難做盤問」。郭官又批評控方，「佢（口供）籠統講，你就詳細問。你要佢心路歷程，恐怕你都係叫佢做返份口供啦」。"},{"pid":"fca40cbbe6021ef2969f9ba8fee212fd2846691e","tid":2167672,"uid":274532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T09:02:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdb19ad284dc8c10d40a98339bf53f59d922c593","tid":2167672,"uid":185656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T09:03:25.000Z","msg":"痱滋狗"},{"pid":"3698d459d733cb91c0109a06df57fef839af48d0","tid":2167672,"uid":76609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T09:05:12.000Z","msg":"生滋狗"},{"pid":"96e76a114c1eb8154bb4342c7612a2b02847b7ee","tid":2167672,"uid":5490,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T09:08:53.000Z","msg":"有無圓月彎刀？<br />\n<br />\n見到佢一路追，一路追，一路追，一路追，一路追"},{"pid":"1ca441fc2e49f78ada1e282271237b2f55fb3979","tid":2167672,"uid":279333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T09:12:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}